      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit maintains crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies, with the double VANOS system functioning within factory tolerances. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels, managed by the M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to reinforced subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and a refreshed suspension setup utilizing Bilstein dampers. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its status, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the visceral, high-RPM engagement enthusiasts demand.",
